caption.p: Protein–protein interaction network of differentially expressed messenger RNAs (mRNAs) related to ovary development. ( A) Probable functional network of mRNAs in H1 vs H3. ( B) Probable functional network of mRNAs in H3 vs H8. H1, H3 and H8 represent 1, 3 and 8 months old ovaries, respectively.
